# XXXIX.

1\. Killing domestic or wild animals are crimes degrading to a mixed
caste.

2\. He who has committed a crime degrading to a mixed caste shall eat
barley-gruel for a month (if he has committed it knowingly), or perform
the penance K*rikkh*râtik*rikkh*ra (if he has committed it unawares).

\[35. Regarding the penances called *K*ândrâya*n*a and Parâka see below,
XLVIII and XLVII, 18.

